Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "Right, Commandantâ€”I've noticed as well. These guards seem to be pushing us further inside intentionally.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "Still, we can't do anything even though we have figured that out. Commandant, I hate being played.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'We have to be even calmer in this situation.', 3: '7', 4: "We're slowly entering the enemy's trap.", 5: '7'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "I'll come up with an emergency plan immediately. We have to be prepared for the worst-case scenario...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Iron Maiden', 3: "To wear the Queen's shackles is an honor bestowed to you and that lowly creature by your side...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: '...How did she appear so close to us?!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Iron Maiden', 3: 'As the royal guard of Her Majesty, I command you, Construct... Arrest the human by your side, and hand me the human!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Watch your feet, Commandant! The guards are crawling out from the trapdoors below us!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Iron Maiden', 3: "Defy Her Majesty's will, and you too will be shackled, regardless if you are a fierce Construct warrior or not!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 3: 'A holographic projection of Liv appears on your comms...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Iron Maiden', 3: 'My servants! Take down the Construct and human before me!', 4: '1'}
